ttcut-ng (0.51.0-1~forky) forky; urgency=medium

  * ttcut-demux: Add audio padding at end to match video duration (like ProjectX)
    - Reduces A/V drift from 372ms to under 20ms
    - Achieves ProjectX-quality A/V synchronization
  * ttcut-demux: Add audio trim at start for A/V offset correction
  * ttcut-demux: Add duration mismatch detection and reporting in .info file
  * Preview widget: Fix button order (Zurück/Start/Vor)

