ttcut-ng (0.50.2-1~forky) forky; urgency=medium

  * Current Frame: Play button with audio playback (embedded mpv)
  * Preview dialog: Next/Previous cut navigation buttons (Vor/Zurück)
  * A/V sync offset applied to all output formats (TS, MKV, MP4)
  * User warning when clicking "New Project" with unsaved changes
  * Keyboard shortcuts: j/k for frame, g/G for home/end, [ ] for cut-in/out
  * Warning dialog if audio and video length differ
  * Help menu: Keyboard shortcuts reference dialog
  * Fixed duplicate ES file deletion in mplex provider

